        "text": "As transgressors; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " i.e. to be transgressors, viz. of the whole law, as fellows. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
